Quest:All Hail Azoth

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
None
Note: Level 30 is needed to start this quest.

Given By: Abner K. Doodle

Giver Location: The Commons
This is a side quest.

Goals:
Learn about Azoth

(completes automatically upon accepting)


Hand In: Completes Automatically

Reward:

0
0


Leads to:

None

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to All Hail Azoth should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to All Hail Azoth in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
